Package: genescout
Title: Agentic Evidence-Review Workbench for Gene Prioritization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Samuel", "Bharti", email = "sbharti@uab.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: GeneScout is an agentic, R-native evidence-review workbench for
    research genomics. It investigates one or more candidate gene lists against a
    disease context and returns a disease-informed, plausibility-ranked shortlist
    with the supporting evidence, the uncertainties, and recommended next
    experiments. Built on ellmer for provider-agnostic LLM orchestration and httr2
    for public bio-database access. Research use only.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
